ould keep open until 9 oclock That census was carefully taken and when the figures were com piled It showed the city had a popula tion of about 17000 After the government census was taken last spring a school census of the city was taken This latter cen sus was also disappointing for It show ed"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-16T23:03:15.403Z", "group": ["ndnp/au", "university-of-alabama-tuscaloosa-al-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84020645/1910-12-20/ed-1/?sp=7", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_andrews_ver01:data:sn84020645:00513684381:1910122001:1302/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=439&w=310", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_andrews_ver01:data:sn84020645:00513684381:1910122001:1302/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=878&w=621", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/au/batch_au_andrews_ver01/data/sn84020645/00513684381/1910122001/1302.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["alabama", "montgomery county", "montgomery", "united states"], "location_city": ["montgomery"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["montgomery"], "location_state": ["alabama"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["1", "3", "0", "sn84020645", "6", "5", "8", "0000000007", "4"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn84020645"], "number_page": ["0000000007"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "5", "1", "3", "6", "8", "4", "3", "8", "1"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Saturday morning", "Montgomery advertiser and Alabama journal", "Montgomery advertiser/Alabama journal", "Daily advertiser"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the montgomery advertiser (montgomery, ala.) 1885-1982"